          "reviewBody": "I saw many schools for my child but I don't understand  ..then I go to Ramagya school, I liked the school..nd the environment and  teachers were seriously very helpful for me a lot ....  There is an experienced teacher in every school, but the behaviour of the children and parents as well as their  more important for me..and every school focuses on the studies of the children for the results of its school\nBut RAMAGYA school teacher's Best 😊",
          "publisher": {
