          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My son is studying in Ramagya School Noida since from nursery class and now he has completed 8th standard. Teachers are supporting in nature and ready to help at any time. My son got opportunity to participate in various science project competitions. Recently he received Rs. 10000/- award through Department of Science and Technology Inspire-Manak program for his science project. My son's skills and learning also enhanced through various activities performed in school. I am thankful to Ramagya School.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
